comments: Capela (ATL) legally contests Irving's (BKN) jump shot attempt.
Hunter (ATL) and Claxton (BKN) briefly engage and separate during the rebound.
Young (ATL) brings the ball to a pause as his hand is completely underneath the ball during his dribble. He then continues his dribble thereafter.
Young (ATL) makes marginal contact as his hand brushes Durant (BKN) during the dunk attempt.
Mills (BKN) initiates contact with Young (ATL) on the perimeter and uses two hands to drive him off his spot, affecting his FOM.
Replay review confirmed that Huerter's (ATL) shot made contact with the rim and the 24-second shot clock violation was overturned. ATL maintained possession of the ball.
Bogdanovic (ATL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Mills (BKN) as he firms up and absorbs the contact during the pick.
Durant (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Huerter (ATL) as he firms up and absorbs the contact during the pick.
Claxton (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Hunter (ATL) as he firms up and absorbs the contact during the pick.
Claxton (BKN) commits a take foul on Young (ATL).
Young (ATL) makes marginal contact as he slides his hands off Irving's (BKN) body during the driving shot attempt.
Edwards (BKN) commits a take foul on Hunter (ATL).
Mills (BKN) commits a take foul on Young (ATL).
